This property is located on the corner of Queens Road and Harris Road, Five Dock.

Office spaces available ranging from 80sqm* – 1,282sqm* 

The building is well serviced with gym, café and car wash facilities.

LOCATION:
Five Dock is a suburb in the inner-west of Sydney. The subject property is located 10km* west of the Sydney Central Business District, 10km* from the Parramatta CBD and 2.5km* east of the entrance to the M4 Motorway, in the Local Government Area of the City of Canada Bay.

Five Dock lies between Parramatta Road and the City West Link to the south and Hen and Chicken Bay, on the Parramatta River, along with the suburbs of Wareemba and Russell Lea, to the north. Five Dock is an increasingly popular suburb offering spectacular views to the city to which it is linked by both roads and ferry.

The subject building is located on the high profile corner of Queens Road and Harris Road, directly opposite Rosebank College High School. This is an extremely busy intersection as Queens Road is an important alternate route to Parramatta Road for both east and west bound traffic. There is undercover parking within the building with access off Harris Road and with Five Dock's close proximity to the CBD the site is serviced by public buses, with a stop directly in front of the building.

Contact the exclusive agent today for more information.
